  @contract  selection must be exactly one grid column; multi-col selection is a no-op  @ 2702
  @invariant  a 1-col block stays contiguous when it lands on the destination col  @ 2703
  @contract  cursor follows to the destination column (single event and selection alike)  @ 2704
  @contract  refuse if dest col has any onset in source's row extent (note: note-on; else any event)  @ 2705
  @invariant  source's row extent = selection's [r1,r2] for a block, moved event's onset row for a single  @ 2706
  @invariant  tails (either direction) clipped by tm's tail pass; never block  @ 2707
  @contract  reentrancy-guarded; bails on no-take (page shows placeholder)  @ 3643
  @contract  takeChanged=true resets ec and re-reads resolution/length/timeSigs  @ 3644
  @contract  grid + ctx rebuild each call; pushMute at end  @ 3645
